68
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:13,560
are actually colorful?

69
00:06:15,279 --> 00:06:16,959
Yet people misunderstand them

70
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,439
and depict them as black.

71
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,759
Just say the word,

72
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:26,920
