73
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,040
You know

74
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:31,720
I can't leave.

75
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,759
Don't worry about your family.

76
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,800
I'll get them out.

77
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,360
