Ya'er.

111
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,720
Ya'er.

112
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,200
You woke up.

113
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,600
Ling.

114
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:14,560
Come on.

115
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,679
