116
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,600
I'm fine now.

117
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:31,559
I'm fine.

118
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,440
Sun Er's medical notes

119
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,600
