126
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:04,120
I was so scared.

127
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:08,159
I thought you might actually die.

128
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,919
I don't mind dying

129
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,559
